{"title":"献给太阳（外一首）","authors":["苏敏"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":9,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给太阳（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏敏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁，游戏于白云之上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶起一片春意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让小溪流也灿烂也歌唱？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁，曾经沉睡在礁石之中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放任蓝色的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罩住心窗里那一柱细香？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁，按着音乐的节拍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要黄昏爬上花墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边又悄悄地约着星光？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁，正摇动生命的奖旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请来金黄的麦浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天地间再作亿万次交响？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁，浸染片片温柔的秋叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路吻遍爱情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵出脚下一层层追想？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是谁，令串串笑声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倚在岁月的肩头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披阅这重重叠叠的人造天宫？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花炮举起团圆夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一盏红灯笼照耀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你思念，我思念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"短短的边境线两边呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋千上的你，弯弯笑眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“请勿忘我”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦！我听见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邮车攀上航空机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传送你南国心香一片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看海，我看海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可念我们踏在岸上空还愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搜集所有的快乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"系风铃，挂上你窗前枕前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咦，你早听见。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}